## Data Licenses

This software uses data from multiple sources with different licenses:

### LINZ NZ Addresses
Source: Land Information New Zealand (LINZ)
License: CC BY 4.0 (Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International)
Link: https://data.linz.govt.nz/

### Stats NZ Geographic Boundaries
Source: Stats NZ Tatauranga Aotearoa
License: CC BY 4.0 (Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International)
Link: https://datafinder.stats.govt.nz/

### TradeMe Locality Data
Source: TradeMe Property Listings
Usage: Market-friendly suburb names for improved user experience
Note: Locality names only, no proprietary data included

When using this software, you must comply with the CC BY 4.0 license terms
for LINZ and Stats NZ data, which requires attribution when using their datasets.
